@{fg highlight}@{"SetAHSystem" link "Einstellungen-14"}@{fg text} @{fg fill}MODE/A/N@{fg text}
MODE is 0 (S=0°) or 1 (N=0°).

@{fg highlight}@{"SetObtainPen" link "Einstellungen-14"}@{fg text} @{fg fill}PRECISION/A/N@{fg text}
PRECISION from 0 (GUI) to 3 (EXACT).

